recipesJson.name: Peanut butter jelly man . (using Jam on toast V2 )
recipesJson.author: BigRed
recipesJson.description: Ok so in my opinion jam on toast V2 isn’t bad at all it’s actually really good the OG is good to but the only real difference i get is the O.G is a little harsh and has a slight more toast but not by much . so for all you wondering V2 is still VERY good.
